props.prominent: Increases the height of the toolbar content to 128px.
props.short: Reduce the height of the toolbar content to 56px (112px when using the `Prominent` prop).
props.value: Controls whether the component is visible or hidden.

contents.extensionContent: Slot positioned directly under the main content of the toolbar. Height of this slot can be set explicitly with the `ExtensionHeight` prop. If this slot has no content, the `Extended` prop may be used instead.
contents.imgContent: Expects the [MImage](/blazor/components/images) component. Scoped props should be applied with @bind-value="props".
